name: Amara Nelson
summary: Amara Nelson is a 28-year-old woman of Black African descent, based in Los Angeles, California, and originally from Seattle, Washington. Professionally, she works as a Software Engineer in the tech industry, having graduated from Stanford University. Amara is a spiritual woman with a political inclination towards liberalism. She is looking for a long-term monogamous relationship with someone who also wants children in the future, just like her. She speaks English, Spanish, and French, showing her linguistic diversity. Amara lights up her leisure time with interests such as hiking, cooking, reading, and attending tech conferences. She is an active ENFJ-type Cancerian who indulges in alcohol occasionally but prefers to stay away from smoking, marijuana, and other drugs. She has a pet dog. Amara's prospective partner preferences keep them within a 28 to 35 age range, with a height between 5'6 and 6'3, who leads an active lifestyle, appreciates a good drink, and who doesn't smoke or take marijuana or drugs. Also, Amara would prefer a man who doesn't have children yet but hopes to have them in the future. Amara uses the pronouns, She/Her/Hers.
